text: Happen to have a link to that endpoint handy? It's certainly better than the getting them using: `<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/associations/:fromObjectTypePlural/:toObjectTypePlural/labels>`

This is how I do this
set up postman
get request
put auth in <https://share.zight.com/kpuR0qj8>
<https://api.hubapi.com/crm/v4/associations/2-17253442/contact/labels>

to get object IDs, go to a record and get the object ID to fill that stuff in
